    "The findings and recommendations presented here provide valuable insights for organizations seeking to bolster their cybersecurity defenses in an increasingly interconnected world.",
    "Ongoing research and adaptation to evolving threats will remain crucial in maintaining effective network security.",
    "Organizations should consider employing a combination of models for intrusion detection, leveraging the strengths of each model type.",
    "Regular updates and retraining of models are essential to adapt evolving intrusion techniques.",
    "Integration of anomaly-based and signature-based detection methods can enhance overall network security."
